Class TransactionalTopologyBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.storm.transactional.TransactionalTopologyBuilder
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class TransactionalTopologyBuilder
extends Object

    Trident subsumes the functionality provided by transactional topologies, so this class is deprecated.
